    "how_h418": "Level Up",
    "how_p19": "MathMate doesn't just solve problems — it builds understanding through a repeatable learning loop designed to close gaps and grow skills over time.",
    "how_p20": "Before MathMate can help you improve, it needs to understand your starting point. A short diagnostic quiz reveals which topics you've mastered, which feel shaky, and where the real gaps are hiding.",
    "how_p21": "10-minute quiz across core topics. See your score, spot the gaps, get your roadmap — immediately.",
    "how_p22": "A visual breakdown of every topic — green means solid, orange means review, red means learn first.",
    "how_p23": "Snap a photo of any math problem or browse your recommended concepts. MathMate breaks everything into clear, step-by-step explanations — always telling you not just WHAT, but WHY and HOW.",
    "how_p24": "Point your camera at any handwritten or printed problem. Get a full step-by-step solution in under 10 seconds.",
    "how_p25": "Ask anything. Get an explanation in your language. The chat remembers your session and builds on it.",
    "how_p26": "Understanding is one thing. Applying it is another. After learning a concept, MathMate gives you targeted practice questions to confirm mastery — so you don't move forward on shaky ground.",
    "how_p27": "Multiple-choice questions with real explanations. Every wrong answer is a learning moment, not just a mark lost.",
    "how_p28": "Bookmark solutions you want to revisit. Build your own personal revision library for exam prep.",
    "how_p29": "MathMate tracks everything — quiz scores, solved problems, revisited concepts, streak days — and turns it into a clear picture of how you're growing. Then it adjusts your roadmap accordingly.",
    "how_p30": "Clear charts showing topic-level growth over time. See exactly how far you've come and what's next.",
    "how_p31": "As your skills grow, your roadmap updates automatically — always pointing you to the highest-impact next step.",
    "how_p32": "Each pass through the loop adds data. More data means a smarter roadmap. A smarter roadmap means faster progress. MathMate compounds.",
    "how_p33": "Quiz results pinpoint exactly where the learning needs to happen.",
    "how_p34": "Step-by-step explanations and chat build understanding at the root.",
    "how_p35": "Practice questions verify understanding before moving forward.",
    "how_p36": "Roadmap updates, unlocking harder topics built on solid foundations.",
    "how_p37": "Download MathMate and take the 10-minute diagnostic quiz. Your personalised roadmap is ready the moment you finish.",
    "how_li38": "Grade-level quiz tailored to your school year",
    "how_li39": "Topic-by-topic breakdown of strengths and weaknesses",
    "how_li40": "Instant results — no waiting, no judgment",
    "how_li41": "The starting point for your personalised roadmap",
    "how_li42": "Snap a problem with your camera — solved in seconds",
    "how_li43": "Every step explained in plain English",
    "how_li44": "Ask follow-up questions in the chat",
    "how_li45": "Prerequisite concepts highlighted so nothing gets skipped",
    "how_li46": "Topic-specific quizzes after each concept",
    "how_li47": "Instant feedback with explanations for every answer",
    "how_li48": "Wrong answers trigger a micro-lesson on the spot",
    "how_li49": "Streak rewards to keep motivation high",
